{"results":[{"aya":"036","id":1838,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"他说：我的主啊！求你对我缓刑，直到人类复活之日。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"037","id":1839,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"主说：你确是被缓刑","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"038","id":1840,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"到可知的日期。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"039","id":1841,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"他说：我的主啊！你已判定我是迷误的，所以我誓必在大地上以罪恶诱惑他们，我必定要使他们一同迷误。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"040","id":1842,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"除非他们中你所选拔的仆人。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"041","id":1843,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"主说：这是我应当维持的正路。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"042","id":1844,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"我的仆人，你对他们绝无权力，除非那些顺从你的迷误者。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":15,"previousPage":"/zh/s015-5.json","nextPage":"/zh/s015-7.json"}}